What “PortableServer” means
===========================
“Portable” means:
The server implementation should work across different ORB (Object Request Broker) implementations
Not tied to a specific vendor

It belongs to the broader CORBA framework (Common Object Request Broker Architecture) and specifically provides server-side APIs.

